<topic id='element_decision_to_treat_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: DECISION TO TREAT DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_decision_to_treat_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">DECISION TO TREAT DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_decision_to_treat_date">DECISION TO TREAT DATE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_decision_to_treat_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">DECISION TO TREAT DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the date that a decision was taken to treat a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>'s condition with a 
              <xref outputclass="attribute"
               keyref="attribute_radiotherapy_treatment_modality">RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT MODALITY</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Where the treatment is being undertaken as part of a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_cancer_treatment_period">Cancer Treatment Period</xref>
 and the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_cancer_treatment_modality">CANCER TREATMENT MODALITY</xref>
 is National Code 
              <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_teletherapy">Teletherapy</xref>'</i>
 or 
              <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                  keyref="business_definition_brachytherapy">Brachytherapy</xref>'</i>, the 
              <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_decision_to_treat_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">DECISION TO TREAT DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the same as the 
              <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_cancer_treatment_period_start_date">CANCER TREATMENT PERIOD START DATE</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
</body>
